name:                pseudocodeCompiler
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            A bytecode compiler for pseudocode
-- description:
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Felix Giese
maintainer:          s4fegies@uni-trier.de
